name: Dorsil
content:
Dorsil was a male Twi'lek Pilgrim who lived on Tython during the Cold War between the Sith Empire and the Galactic Republic.
A Twi'lek male, Dorsil was among the many Pilgrims who followed Matriarch Kolovish to the planet Tython in the aftermath of the Great Galactic War. Assisting in the establishment of Kalikori village, Dorsil was a merchant who traded specialty goods with visitors and citizens of Kalikori.
Dorsil was removed from the game in update 6.2 of Star Wars: The Old Republic: Onslaught. He was later brought back to the game in update 7.1 of Star Wars: The Old Republic: Legacy of the Sith.
